[Miscellaneous Codes\Aggressive Enemies / Allies]
author=Ryan Toluchanian
description=This code works on all levels, but its effect is most visible in Yellow Turban level. In Yellow Turban level, with the code on, the enemy leader Jiao comes down the hill and with all enemy units converges on the allied leader. Enemies in all levels are more aggressive. Code is an enemy action modifier.
patch=1,EE,1023CFE8,extended,00000001

[Aggressive Enemies/Allies]
author=Code Master, StalkerX, Ryan Toluchanian
description=
patch=1,EE,1023CFE8,extended,00000001

[All Special Troop Events Occur]
author=Code Master, StalkerX, Ryan Toluchanian
description=
patch=1,EE,1021F598,extended,00000001

[Miscellaneous Codes\Allow For Special Weapon Body Guards]
author=Ryan Toluchanian
description=Code overrides default for any in-battle general's default body guards for whatever certain battle you play, meaning you get the default weapon body guards! So, for example if you play as Xiahou Dun in Chi Bi you get his trident weapon body guards!!! The guards are stat-wise the same as your regular guards but they get to use the other weapons that the default AI general's guards get, like tridents and Dragon blades. Only a slight problem with the code, is that you may start off in a different place than usual. It also only works for in-battle generals, if a general is not normally in a battle you chose to play, the code won't work for him.)
patch=1,EE,1021D14C,extended,00000001

[Allow For Special Weapon Bodyguards]
author=Code Master, StalkerX, Ryan Toluchanian
description=
patch=1,EE,1021D14C,extended,00000001

[Miscellaneous Codes\Alter Button Attacks]
author=Ryan Toluchanian
description=
patch=1,EE,1022B874,extended,00000001

[Miscellaneous Codes\Attack Frenzy!]
author=Ryan Toluchanian
description=With this code, enemies and allies attack each other with a lot more force and action than usual.
patch=1,EE,1022C180,extended,00000001
patch=1,EE,1023CFE8,extended,00000001

