[Miscellaneous Codes\Choose Enemies/allies Fighting Style]
author=RyanToluchanian
description=Note: Whatever character you choose to play as, most enemies/allies will have their fighting style! Meaning you can now fight multiple Lu Bu like enemies in any level!
patch=1,EE,1021DB44,extended,00000001

