[Miscellaneous Codes\Game Thinks You're An AI Bot]
author=Ryan Toluchanian
description=Just for fun, can't complete levels while code is on. Play as Xiahou Dun, if Xiahou Dun doesn't work on a level, use Guan Yu. Any in-battle officer/general should work though for whatever certain battle you play. Enemy/allied leaders won't work though. Also you have increased moving and attack speed. Don't use R1 button, arrows, the game will freeze if you do.)
patch=1,EE,1021D120,extended,00000001

