[Miscellaneous Codes\Play As He Jin Or Twin]
author=Ryan Toluchanian
description=WARNING!!! Don't EVER save the game after a battle is done while the code is on!!! Safe to use code as long as you don't save the game. To play as He Jin in the Yellow Turban level, chose to play as Zhao Yun, instead though of Zhao Yun you'll actually play as He Jin when the gameplay starts! Also for any allied (left of screen) side in-battle generals you can have a twin, like two Xiahou Duns in the Turban level.
patch=1,EE,1021D258,extended,00000001

[Miscellaneous Codes\Play As Unplayable Characters]
author=Ryan Toluchanian
description=Note: WARNING!!! Don't EVER save the game after a battle is done while the code is on!!! Safe to use code as long as you don't save the game.Code only works for left of screen side, to play as a new character select from list below and that character you select will change into the other character once gameplay starts. I've only tested out 9 characters, you can test others if you want to play as another character other than the listed below...
